acceptance_criteria: Every plan step is completed with linked pm evidence and the feature closes only after merged-master proof
definition_of_ready: Feature scope and child issues created from duplicate-safe evidence
value: "Keeps official research, local implementation, and hosted review as one auditable delivery chain"
impact: Prevents partial completion at local or PR-only state
