confidence: high
release: 2026.7.22
resolution: "All nine delivery steps completed; PR #60 merged with protected checks, complete bot acknowledgement, exact-master release verification, and live read-only proof."
expected_result: Reviewed API parity delivery is merged and verified on master with complete linked evidence.
actual_result: "PR #60 merged at 8c1c67e; all protected contexts were green, no actionable bot findings remained, and exact-master release/live gates passed."
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T20:44:19.131Z",codex-root,Delivery step 6 is active on PR #60. Hosted checks and full paginated review inventory will be recorded before merge; any push will retrigger every requested review agent.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T21:00:35.810Z",codex-root,"GitHub may not enqueue push workflows for a squash merge performed through automation even when the workflows include master push triggers. Keep pull-request protection authoritative, retain an exact-merge local release gate, and expose workflow_dispatch so the final master SHA can receive hosted attestation explicitly."
close_reason: "All ordered research, implementation, validation, review, merge, and exact-master proof steps completed."
plan_mode: approved
plan_decisions[2]{ts,author,decision,rationale,evidence}:
  "2026-07-21T19:00:05.325Z",codex-root,Keep raw ws call as the forward-compatible full API surface and add typed helpers only for stable high-value discovery contracts.,Home Assistant WebSocket commands are dynamic and integration-dependent; typed affordances should improve agent UX without pretending the finite CLI can freeze every command.,Official WebSocket docs describe generic command envelopes and current target helper commands; existing ws call accepts arbitrary types.
  "2026-07-21T21:00:13.808Z",codex-root,Expose manual CI dispatch for exact merged-head verification.,"Protected pull-request checks prove the proposed head, while workflow_dispatch lets maintainers attest the exact post-merge master SHA when GitHub does not enqueue a push run.","PR #60 merged as 8c1c67e; exact merge release verification passed locally, but no push check suite was created."
plan_discoveries[1]{ts,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:00:04.305Z",codex-root,Live settings validation fails before network I/O because Undici 8 rejects request-level throwOnError.
